title: Week 14 preview & Vikings vs. Cardinals recap
itunes:title: Week 14 preview & Vikings vs. Cardinals recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – welcome in NFL Media’s Amber Theoharis as they go game-by-game breaking down each Week 14 matchup. But first, the heroes recap the Cardinals 23-20 victory over the Vikings to clinch a playoff spot in a game that went down to the wire.
